OL,3,CDefiant Starmer set for key meeting
OL,4,Cwith Streeting ahead of King's Speech
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is set to meet Health
OL,7,FSecretary Wes Streeting, one of his
OL,8,Fkey rivals for leadership, on
OL,9,FWednesday, as the prime minister
OL,10,Fattempts to head off an attempt to
OL,11,Fforce him to resign.
OL,13,FIt comes after a tumultuous few days
OL,14,Fin which numerous ministers and aides
OL,15,Fresigned, and almost 100 of his MPs
OL,16,Fcalled for him to resign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
