OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778746039
OL,3,CDefiant Starmer set for key meeting
OL,4,Cwith Streeting ahead of King's Speech
OL,6,FBut as of Wednesday morning, the
OL,7,Fimmediate threat to Starmer's
OL,8,Fleadership appears to have passed,
OL,9,Fwith most of his Cabinet staying
OL,10,Fpublicly loyal and over 100
OL,11,Fbackbenchers signing a pledge saying
OL,12,Fhe should stay.
OL,14,FThe crisis was triggered after the
OL,15,Fdisastrous results in last week's
OL,16,Flocal elections, which saw Labour lose
OL,17,Fover a thousand seats, mostly to
OL,18,FReform and the Greens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
