OL,3,CDefiant Starmer set for key meeting
OL,4,Cwith Streeting ahead of King's Speech
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, he will meet Streeting,
OL,7,Fseen as one of the key challengers to
OL,8,Fhis leadership from the right of the
OL,9,Fparty, ahead of the King's Speech.
OL,11,FAccording to The Guardian, the health
OL,12,Fsecretary was backing down from
OL,13,Flaunching an immediate leadership bid,
OL,14,Fwith reports suggesting he doesn't
OL,15,Fhave the numbers to launch a challenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
