OL,3,CDefiant Starmer set for key meeting
OL,4,Cwith Streeting ahead of King's Speech
OL,6,FStarmer told his Cabinet the country
OL,7,F"expects us to get on with governing"
OL,8,Fand "that is what I am doing", but
OL,9,Favoided being directly challenged as
OL,10,Fhe declined to discuss his leadership
OL,11,Fduring the gathering or meet critics
OL,12,Findividually afterwards.
OL,14,FHe said he would only speak to
OL,15,Fministers one-to-one about his fate,
OL,16,Fbut did not do so once Cabinet
OL,17,Fconcluded, according to sources.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@eO]pD@EOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
