OL,3,CDefiant Starmer set for key meeting
OL,4,Cwith Streeting ahead of King's Speech
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWhile Streeting is not expected to say
OL,12,Fanything after Wednesday's meeting
OL,13,Fthat could distract from the King's
OL,14,FSpeech, Politico reported that
OL,15,FBuckingham Palace had privately told
OL,16,FNumber 10 they do not want the King to
OL,17,Fbe dragged into the conversation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
